&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Each fulfilment session contains an ordered list of entities that must be completed:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Example: Event with form → payment → completion&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>List&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>FulfilmentEntity&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> entities &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> FormsFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Collect attendee info&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> StripeFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Process payment&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> EndFulfilmentEntity &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Redirect to success page&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
