&lt;h3>Multi-Ticket Forms&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="multi-ticket-forms">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#multi-ticket-forms" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>For events requiring multiple tickets, we create &lt;strong>one form entity per ticket&lt;/strong>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">// 3 tickets = 3 form entities + 1 payment + 1 end&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>List&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>FulfilmentEntity&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> entities &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> FormsFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Ticket 1 info&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> FormsFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Ticket 2 info &lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> FormsFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Ticket 3 info&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> StripeFulfilmentEntity, &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Single payment&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> EndFulfilmentEntity &lt;span style="color:#75715e">// Success&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
